article.story: THIBODAUX, La. -- — Jamal West and Chase Forte scored 17 points apiece and Nicholls defeated Northwestern State 73-66 on Monday night. West also had seven rebounds, five assists, and three blocks for the Colonels (12-10, 7-2 Southland Conference). Gray made three 3-pointers, adding five rebounds and three steals. Diante Smith scored 16. Cliff Davis led the Demons (6-17, 4-6) with 25 points. Chase Forte added 17 points and Duane Posey scored 11 with six rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
